Extract simulation results

Source: R/meta--get-results.R
get_results.Rd

Extract ERAHUMED simulation results from an erahumed_simulation object.

Usage

get_results(
  simulation,
  component = c("hydrology", "exposure", "risk"),
  element = c("lake", "ditch", "cluster")
)

Arguments

simulation

[erahumed_simulation]
The simulation object being modified.

component

[character(1)]
The simulation component to be extracted. Either "hydrology", "exposure", or "risk".

element

[character(1)]
The landscape element for which simulation results are requested. Either "lake", "ditch", or "cluster".

Value

A data.frame.
